{"title":"artitalk美化","uid":"9b4f9982061d1777380ef553da7bb8cc","slug":"artitalk美化","date":"2021-07-11T08:41:56.000Z","updated":"2021-08-10T16:05:45.607Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/artitalk美化.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/05/30/4kbizhi/2.jpg","content":"<p>artitalk背景色单调且不好看<br>于是今天就来折腾ta</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>点击进入项目说明文档，地址：<a href=\"https://artitalk.js.org/doc.html\">https://artitalk.js.org/doc.html</a><br>发现可以自定义配置项<br>配置项说明文档：<a href=\"https://artitalk.js.org/settings.html\">https://artitalk.js.org/settings.html</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>由于本主题已经集成artitalk，所以只要修改主题中的几个配置就行</p>\n<h2 id=\"matery\"><a href=\"#matery\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"matery\"></a>matery</h2><p>在主题配置文件中找到artitalk配置，修改如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\"># 说说 https:&#x2F;&#x2F;artitalk.js.org&#x2F;\nartitalk:\n  enable: true\n  appId: 在leancloud中查看\n  appKey: 在leancloud中查看\n  color1: linear-gradient(45deg, rgb(251 205 205) 35%, rgb(138 195 255) 85%)  #说说背景色1\n  color2: linear-gradient(45deg, rgb(191 255 209) 15%, rgb(154 228 245) 85%)   #说说背景色2\n  color3: rgb(0, 0, 0) #说说字体颜色<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>同步在/themes/matery/layout/_widget/artitalk.ejs中引用主题配置</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&lt;script type&#x3D;&quot;text&#x2F;javascript&quot; src&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;unpkg.com&#x2F;artitalk&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;\n&lt;div id&#x3D;&quot;artitalk_main&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n&lt;script&gt;\n    new Artitalk(&#123;\n        appId: &#39;&lt;%- theme.artitalk.appId %&gt;&#39;,\n        appKey: &#39;&lt;%- theme.artitalk.appKey %&gt;&#39;,\n        color1: &#39;&lt;%- theme.artitalk.color1 %&gt;&#39;,\n        color2: &#39;&lt;%- theme.artitalk.color2 %&gt;&#39;,\n        color3: &#39;&lt;%- theme.artitalk.color3 %&gt;&#39;,\n        atEmoji: &#123;\n                  baiyan: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;baiyan.png&quot;,\n                  bishi: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;bishi.png&quot;,\n                  bizui: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;bizui.png&quot;,\n                  chan: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;chan.png&quot;,\n                  daku: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;daku.png&quot;,\n                  dalao: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;dalao.png&quot;,\n                  dalian: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;dalian.png&quot;,\n                  dianzan: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;dianzan.png&quot;,\n                  doge: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;doge.png&quot;,\n                  facai: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;facai.png&quot;,\n                  fadai: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;fadai.png&quot;,\n                  fanu: &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Artitalk&#x2F;Artitalk-emoji&#x2F;fanu.png&quot;,\n                &#125;,\n                \n    &#125;)\n&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>成功折腾完毕<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/11/artitalkmeihua/1.png\"> </p>\n","text":"artitalk背景色单调且不好看于是今天就来折腾ta 点击进入项目说明文档，地址